high_descs: Turn right to walk into the kitchen to reach the sink.
Pick up the mug from the sink.
Turn around to face the microwave on the left.
Heat the mug in the microwave and take it out.
Head to the room on the left and walk up to the shelf on the right above the table.
Put the mug in the left shelf.
anns.task_desc: Put the heated mug in the shelf.

high_descs: Turn right, go to the sink.
Turn around, go to the microwave, turn left.
Open the microwave. Place the mug on the left side of the microwave. Turn it on for five seconds. Open the door. Take out the mug. Close the door.
Turn right, exit and cross to the left. When you reach the shelf, turn left. When you enter the room, turn right.
Place the mug on the shelf on the left side.
anns.task_desc: Find a mug, heat it. Place it on the shelf.
